## Competitive Differentiators

Three capabilities not addressed by major frameworks:
1. **Multi-layer context assembly** (L1) — beyond flat prompts
2. **Feedback translation** (L4) — system errors → model-consumable signals
3. **Entropy management** (L5) — active context quality maintenance

